# Data contract is frozen

`profile.json` and `scan_results.json` shapes are frozen unless the core owner approves.

- Never rename or remove fields — only add new ones.
- Any schema change requires a core-owner review and a CHANGELOG entry.
- Other modules consume the contract but must not alter it.
